\pard\f0\fs28 Stems slender, branched, floating; roots simple. Leaves small, 2-ranked, imbricate, bilobed. Heterosporous; sori in groups of 2 or 4 on the lower lobe of the first leaf of each branch, surrounded by an indusium; larger sori with several microsporangia, smaller sori with 1 megasporangium.
\par

